<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="lb21May1926"><font color="red">21 May 1926</font> <i>SIC</i> (to Lily Bollach): Many thanks. The MS is excellently done. It is no trouble to me to call every evening as my doctor is quite near there. I have revised nearly all and will call tomorrow Saturday [22 May 1926] evening to see if there is any more done. Yes. You are right. The violet ribbon is better. But please use whichever you have. </div>
